         <abstract id="aspace_9625d7884ae62b377319de45e0816680">Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of Western and Southern Asia. Entries for countries, some of which have older place names, include Afghanistan, Bali (Indonesia), Ceylon (Sri Lanka), Formosa (Taiwan), Java (Indonesia), Korea, and Siam (Thailand).</abstract>
